NAME

    Data::QuickMemoPlus::Reader - Extract text from QuickMemo+ LQM export
    files.

SYNOPSIS

        use Data::QuickMemoPlus::Reader qw(lqm_to_str);
        my $memo_text = lqm_to_str('QuickMemo+_191208_220400.lqm');
        
        ## Supress the header text like this:
        $Data::QuickMemoPlus::Reader::suppress_header = 1;

DESCRIPTION

    Data::QuickMemoPlus::Reader is a module that will extract the text
    contents from archived QuickMemo+ memos.

    QuickMemo+ lqm files are in Zip format. This program unzips them,
    parses the json file inside, then extracts the category and memo text
    from the Json file.

    If the filename of the lqm file contains the original timestamp then
    that is placed in the header of the text along with the category name.
    The header can be disabled by setting the package variable
    $suppress_header to 1.

